'''Jyvus Space City''' was one of the largest [[City-ship/Legends|space cities]] surrounding the planet [[Duro/Legends|Duro]].

==History==
During the [[Battle of Duro (Clone Wars)|Battle of Duro]] in [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]], it was one of the first targets captured by the [[Confederate Navy/Legends|Confederate Navy]]. It was made the headquarters for [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]], and its capture allowed the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] to lower Duro's planetary shield, thus facilitating the planet's surrender within the week.

Jyvus did not survive the [[Battle of Duro (Yuuzhan Vong War)|fight]] over Duro during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] in [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]], during which only [[Urrdorf City]] escaped destruction<ref name="Balance Point">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref>.

